column1: Measures of Cross-Sectional Dispersion for Quarterly Forecasts for GDP PRICE INDEX (PGDP)
Dispersion Measure D2 = 75th Percentile Minus 25th Percentile of the Forecasts for Q/Q Growth
P25 = 25th Percentile of the Forecasts for Q/Q Growth
P75 = 75th Percentile of the Forecasts for Q/Q Growth
At Each Survey Date T, the Quarterly Horizons Are T, T+1, T+2, T+3, and T+4
